parameters.name: DestinationCidrBlock
parameters.description: The destination Classless Inter-Domain Routing (CIDR) block of the route entry.

parameters.name: NextHopId
parameters.description: The ID of the next hop.

parameters.name: NextHopType
parameters.description:
The type of next hop of the custom route entry. Valid values:

*   Instance: an ENS instance.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number of the returned page. Valid values: integers that are greater than 0. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Default value: 10. Valid values: 10 to 100.

parameters.name: RouteEntryId
parameters.description: The ID of the route that you want to query.

parameters.name: RouteEntryType
parameters.description:
The route type. Valid values:

*   Custom: custom route
*   System: system route

parameters.name: RouteTableId
parameters.description: The ID of the route table that you want to query.
